  <description>
    <p>Exult is a project to recreate Ultima VII for modern operating systems, using the game's original plot, data, and graphics files.</p>
    <p>Exult Studio is the editor component of the Exult engine suite and, together with the main Exult engine, can be used to create mods for the Ultima VII games or even build entire new games on their engine.</p>
  </description>
